The chosen 8 predicates has 3 {\em easier relations} with a relatively limited no. of O values (parent, child, and sibling) and 5 {\em harder relations} with potentially long O lists (family, friend, opponent, placeHasPerson---i.e., people being at a place, and hasMember---i.e., members of org. or events). Table (ref) gives statistics for our dataset.